"A simple flag option which, when attached to a configuration variable, is"
" used to indicate that the variable has been deprecated and should no "
"longer be used or relied upon, as it may be removed at any time by future"
" releases."
msgstr ""

# 3c5b8fb51c774adfa662a6ac6d90be1f
